#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&parley; is a vocabulary trainer. It helps you to memorize your vocabulary, "
"for example when you are trying to learn a foreign language. &parley; is not "
"limited to language learning but supports a multitude of subjects."
msgstr ""
"&parley; je vaditelj besedišča. Pomaga vam zapomniti besedišče, na primer, "
"ko se poskušate naučiti tujega jezika. &parley; ni omejen na učenje jezikov, "
"temveč podpira številne predmete."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

