#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&parley; is a vocabulary trainer. It helps you to memorize your vocabulary, "
"for example when you are trying to learn a foreign language. You can create "
"your own vocabulary collections with the words you need or select from a "
"great variety of available <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/"
"Parley#Vocabulary_Collections\">Vocabulary Collections</ulink>. There you "
"can find collections containing language vocabulary and also anatomy, music, "
"geography, chemistry or exam preparation."
msgstr ""
"&parley; je vaditelj besedišča. Pomaga vam zapomniti besedišče, na primer, "
"ko se poskušate naučiti tujega jezika. Ustvarite lahko lastne zbirke "
"besedišča z besedami, ki jih potrebujete, ali pa jih izberete iz velikega "
"števila razpoložljivih <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/"
"Parley#Vocabulary_Collections\">Zbirk besedišča</ulink>. Tam lahko najdete "
"zbirke, ki vsebujejo jezikovno besedišče in tudi anatomijo, glasbo, "
"geografijo, kemijo ali priprave na izpite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&parley; is very flexible and uses the <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Flashcard\">flash card learning approach</ulink>. It automatically "
"keeps track of your learning progress. With &parley; you can arrange your "
"vocabulary as you wish, you create your own lessons as needed. But unlike "
"real flash cards you can use different learning methods with &parley;."
msgstr ""
"&parley; je zelo prilagodljiv in uporablja <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Flashcard\">pristop učenja s flash kartico</ulink>. Samodejno "
"spremlja vaš učni napredek. S &parley; lahko svoje besedišče uredite po "
"želji, po potrebi ustvarite svoje lekcije. Toda v nasprotju s pravimi flash "
"karticami lahko s &parley; uporabljate različne učne metode."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Flashcards contain expressions on the front side and their translation on "
"the back. You start with a pile of cards. If you know the translation on a "
"card, you can put it into a second pile of cards. If you did not remember "
"it, you keep it in the first one to try again later."
msgstr ""
"Kartice vsebujejo izraze na sprednji strani in njihov prevod na zadnji "
"strani. Začnete s kupom kart. Če poznate prevod na kartici, ga lahko daste v "
"drugi kup kart. Če se ga niste spomnili, ga shranite v prvo, da poskusite "
"znova pozneje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&parley;'s main focus is not to teach you grammar. However, there are some "
"exercise forms which may help you in this matter."
msgstr ""
"&parley; glavni poudarek ni, da vas nauči slovnice. Vendar pa obstaja nekaj "
"oblik vadbe, ki vam lahko pomagajo pri tej zadevi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&parley; consists of two big parts: <link linkend=\"practice\">Vocabulary "
"Practice</link> and <link linkend=\"vocabulary-editing\">an Editor for "
"Vocabulary Collections</link>."
msgstr ""
"&parley; je sestavljen iz dveh velikih delov: <link linkend=\"practice"
"\">vaja besedišča</link> in <link linkend=\"vocabulary-editing\">urejevalnik "
"za zbirke besedišča</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this manual the term <emphasis>Vocabulary Collection</emphasis> refers to "
"a file that contains <emphasis>Units</emphasis>. Each unit can be a lesson "
"or a collection of lessons nested to any depth. In the rest of this manual "
"we will refer to units rather than lessons since they can be used for other "
"purposes too."
msgstr ""
"V tem priročniku se izraz <emphasis>Zbirka besedišča</emphasis> nanaša na "
"datoteko, ki vsebuje <emphasis>Enote</emphasis>. Vsaka enota je lahko "
"lekcija ali zbirka lekcij, ugnezdenih do poljubne globine. V nadaljevanju "
"tega priročnika se bomo sklicevali na enote in ne lekcije, saj jih je mogoče "
"uporabiti tudi za druge namene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Both, the <guilabel>Editor</guilabel> and the <guilabel>Practice</guilabel> "
"can be reached from the <link linkend=\"practice-overview\">Practice "
"Overview</link>."
msgstr ""
"Do <guilabel>Urejevalnika</guilabel> in <guilabel>Vaj</guilabel> lahko "
"pridete iz <link linkend=\"practice-overview\">Pregleda vadbe</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"practice\">Practice</link> consists of three parts: "
"first the <link linkend=\"practice-overview\">Practice Overview</link> where "
"you choose what to practice. From there you start the actual <link linkend="
"\"practice\">Practice</link> and when you are done, you get a <link linkend="
"\"summary-after-practice\">Summary</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"practice\">Vaja</link> je sestavljena iz treh delov: najprej "
"<link linkend=\"practice-overview\">Pregled vaje</link>, kjer izberete, kaj "
"boste vadili. Od tam začnete dejansko <link linkend=\"practice\">vajo</link> "
"in ko končate, dobite <link linkend=\"summary-after-practice\">Povzetek</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like in all applications try to use the right-click if you explore features "
"and functionality in &parley;. Make click with the &RMB; displays a "
"<quote>context menu</quote> that shows what you can do with your present "
"situation. Try right-clicking units and words to find some options."
msgstr ""
"Kot v vseh aplikacijah poskusite uporabiti desni klik, če raziskujete "
"funkcije in funkcije v &parley;. Kliknite z &RMB; prikaže <quote>kontekstni "
"meni</quote>, ki prikazuje, kaj lahko storite s svojo trenutno situacijo. "
"Poskusite z desnim klikom na enote in besede, da poiščete nekaj možnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Dashboard</title>"
msgstr "<title>Nadzorna plošča</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you first launch &parley; the <guilabel>Dashboard</guilabel> welcomes "
"you."
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič zaženete &parley; vas <guilabel>Nadzorna plošča</guilabel> pozdravi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At first the <guilabel>Dashboard</guilabel> is empty, once you opened some "
"vocabulary collections, it shows you the ones you worked with most recently."
msgstr ""
"Sprva je <guilabel>Nadzorna plošča</guilabel> prazna, ko odprete nekaj zbirk "
"besedišča, vam prikaže tiste, s katerimi ste nazadnje delali."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:110 index.docbook:148 index.docbook:1098 index.docbook:1325
#: index.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid "&parley; main window"
msgstr "&parley; glavno okno"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:113 index.docbook:1101 index.docbook:1421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dashboard with multiple collections"
msgstr "Nadzorna plošča z več zbirkami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A vocabulary collection is a file that contains words and their translations "
"into other languages or other pairs of words and sentences that you want to "
"memorize. The words are organized in units."
msgstr ""
"Zbirka besedišča je datoteka, ki vsebuje besede in njihove prevode v druge "
"jezike ali druge pare besed in stavkov, ki si jih želite zapomniti. Besede "
"so organizirane v enote."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <emphasis>start practicing</emphasis>, click with the &RMB; on the "
"<guilabel>Practice Anyway</guilabel> box on one of the vocabulary collection "
"names in the list. You are taken to the <link linkend=\"practice-overview"
"\">practice overview</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <emphasis>začeti vaditi</emphasis>, kliknite z &RMB; v polju "
"<guilabel>Vseeno vadite</guilabel> na enem od imen zbirk besedišča na "
"seznamu. Preusmerjeni ste na <link linkend=\"practice-overview\">pregled "
"vadbe</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that a small <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"icon-"
"delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Delete</guiicon> icon appears bottom on the left of the collection "
"item. This lets you remove the collection from the list."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da se spodaj na levi prikaže majhna ikona "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"icon-delete.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Izbriši</"
"guiicon> predmeta zbirke. To vam omogoča, da zbirko odstranite s seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you'd like to start your own collection of vocabulary, press on the "
"<guibutton>Create a New Collection...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti lastno zbirko besedišča, pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Ustvari novo zbirko...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also <link linkend=\"open-an-existing-collection\">open a "
"collection</link> if you have it on your computer already but it's not in "
"the list."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako lahko <link linkend=\"open-an-existing-collection\">odprete "
"zbirko</link>, če jo že imate v računalniku, vendar je ni na seznamu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The last button on the <guilabel>Dashboard</guilabel> offers you to download "
"vocabulary collections made by others. When you've created a file that you'd "
"like to share with others, you can easily upload it from the editor."
msgstr ""
"Zadnji gumb na <guilabel>Nadzorni plošči</guilabel> vam ponuja prenos zbirk "
"besedišča, ki so jih ustvarili drugi. Ko ustvarite datoteko, ki jo želite "
"deliti z drugimi, jo lahko preprosto naložite iz urejevalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&parley; comes with different themes, you can switch to a different "
"graphical style in the settings. For further information, see <link linkend="
"\"configure-parley\">Configure &parley;</link>."
msgstr ""
"&parley; prihaja z različnimi temami, lahko v nastavitvah preklopite na drug "
"grafični slog. Za nadaljnje informacije glejte <link linkend=\"configure-"
"parley\">Konfiguriraj &parley;</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open an existing collection"
msgstr "Odpri obstoječo zbirko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Let's suppose your collection is already on your hard disk."
msgstr "Recimo, da je vaša zbirka že na trdem disku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is what the screen will look like the first time you start &parley;:"
msgstr "Takole bo videti zaslon, ko prvič zaženete &parley;:"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Initial screen"
msgstr "Začetni zaslon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press on the <guibutton>Open an Existing Collection...</guibutton> button."
msgstr "Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Odpri obstoječo zbirko...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the file selection dialog, navigate to the folder containing the data "
"file, and select it by clicking on it. Depending on your system the file "
"either opens immediately, or you have to press the <guibutton>Open</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu za izbiro datoteke se pomaknite do mape, ki vsebuje "
"podatkovno datoteko, in jo izberite s klikom nanjo. Odvisno od vašega "
"sistema se datoteka odpre takoj ali pa morate pritisniti gumb "
"<guibutton>Odpri</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>File select dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za izbiro datoteke</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "<caption>File select dialog</caption>"
msgstr "<caption>Pogovorno okno za izbiro datoteke</caption>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now, the file is loaded, and you move on to the <guilabel>Practice Overview</"
"guilabel> screen: see the following section for further details."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj je datoteka naložena in premaknete se na zaslon <guilabel>Pregled vaje</"
"guilabel>: glejte naslednji razdelek za dodatne podrobnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vocabulary Practice"
msgstr "Vaja za besedišče"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start practicing you select a document after starting &parley;. If you "
"have it opened in the editor already, just press the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-start.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Start Practice..."
"</guiicon> icon in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek vaje izberite dokument po zagonu &parley;. Če ste ga že odprli v "
"urejevalniku, samo pritisnite <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"practice-start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Začni vajo...</guiicon> v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Practice Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vadbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before the actual practice starts, you always get to the <guilabel>Practice "
"Overview</guilabel> screen. There are three areas which allow you to choose "
"what to practice:"
msgstr ""
"Preden se dejanska vadba začne, vedno pridete do zaslona <guilabel>Pregled "
"vadbe</guilabel>. Obstajajo tri področja, ki vam omogočajo, da izberete, kaj "
"boste vadili:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "The selection of languages"
msgstr "Izbira jezikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "The selection of the practice mode"
msgstr "Izbira načina vadbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "The selection of the units that also shows your current progress"
msgstr "Izbor enot, ki prikazuje tudi vaš trenutni napredek"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:190 index.docbook:597 index.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configuring the practice</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracija vadbe</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "<caption>Configuring the practice</caption>"
msgstr "<caption>Konfiguracija vadbe</caption>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left you can select the combination of languages you will practice. "
"If you select for example English to French, you will be shown English words "
"and &parley; will ask you to enter the French translations."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani lahko izberete kombinacijo jezikov, ki jih boste vadili. Če "
"izberete na primer angleščino v francoščino, se vam bodo prikazale angleške "
"besede in &parley; vas bo pozval, da vnesete francoske prevode."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below the language selection you choose the <guilabel>Practice Mode</"
"guilabel> section, this determines how the practice will ask you questions."
msgstr ""
"Pod izbiro jezika izberete razdelek <guilabel>Način vadbe</guilabel>, ki "
"določa, kako vam bo vadba postavljala vprašanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Practice Direction</guilabel> drop down list can be used to "
"select the query that will be shown during the practice. The possible "
"choices are the known phrase (<guimenuitem>Known to Learning</guimenuitem>), "
"the learning phrase (<guimenuitem>Learning to Known</guimenuitem>), or the "
"mix of the phrases (<guimenuitem>Mixed Directions</guimenuitem>)."
msgstr ""
"Spustni seznam <guilabel>Navodila za vadbo</guilabel> lahko uporabite za "
"izbiro poizvedbe, ki bo prikazana med vadbo. Možne izbire so znana fraza "
"(<guimenuitem>Znano v učeno</guimenuitem>), učna fraza (<guimenuitem>Učeno v "
"znano</guimenuitem>) ali mešanica besednih zvez (<guimenuitem>Mešana smer</"
"guimenuitem>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the big part on the right, you see the units of the vocabulary "
"collection. You can select which units you want to practice with the check "
"box in front of the unit name. The number of words that each unit contains "
"is shown next to its name. On the right of the name you see your current "
"progress for the unit."
msgstr ""
"V velikem delu na desni vidite enote besedišča. S potrditvenim poljem pred "
"imenom enote lahko izberete, katere enote želite vaditi. Število besed, ki "
"jih vsebuje posamezna enota, je prikazano poleg njenega imena. Na desni "
"strani imena vidite svoj trenutni napredek za enoto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The progress for each unit is displayed as the percentage of the unit "
"completed and the multi-shaded progress bars. The percentage is calculated "
"based on the total number of words in that unit and the confidence level of "
"each word. The progress bars depict the number of words in each confidence "
"level, with a darker shade depicting a higher confidence. A legend can also "
"be seen at the top of the unit selections, in the header. The colors in this "
"legend depict the corresponding colors of the progress bars, from the fully "
"learned words to the words not yet practiced."
msgstr ""
"Napredek za vsako enoto je prikazan kot odstotek dokončane enote in "
"večsenčne vrstice napredka. Odstotek se izračuna na podlagi skupnega števila "
"besed v tej enoti in stopnje zaupanja vsake besede. Vrstice napredka "
"prikazujejo število besed na vsaki stopnji zaupanja, pri čemer temnejši "
"odtenek prikazuje višjo stopnjo zaupanja. Legendo lahko vidite tudi na vrhu "
"izbir enot, v glavi. Barve v tej legendi prikazujejo ustrezne barve vrstic "
"napredka, od povsem naučenih besed do besed, ki jih še niste vadili."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Practice Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija vadbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Configure Practice</guilabel> dialog allows you to specify "
"more advanced settings that will affect the practice."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Konfiguriraj vadbo</guilabel> vam omogoča, da "
"določite naprednejše nastavitve, ki bodo vplivale na vadbo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <link linkend=\"practice-overview\">Practice Overview</link> screen "
"you reach the <guilabel>Configure Practice</guilabel> dialog with the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-setup.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <link linkend=\"advanced-"
"practice-configuration\"><guiicon>Configure Practice...</guiicon></link> "
"icon in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Na zaslonu <link linkend=\"practice-overview\">Pregled vadbe</link> pridete "
"do pogovornega okna <guilabel>Konfiguracija vaje</guilabel> z "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-setup.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <link linkend=\"advanced-"
"practice-configuration\"><guiicon>Konfiguriraj vadbo...</guiicon></link> v "
"orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Practice Settings"
msgstr "Splošne nastavitve vadbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find several general configuration options for the practice in the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> najdete več splošnih konfiguracijskih "
"možnosti za vadbo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:227 index.docbook:258 index.docbook:273 index.docbook:290
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Practice dialog"
msgstr "Konfiguriraj pogovorno okno za vadbo"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:230 index.docbook:1499
#, no-c-format
msgid "General settings page"
msgstr "Stran s splošnimi nastavitvami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "The most important options are:"
msgstr "Najpomembnejše možnosti so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Ignore accents</guilabel>: with this option if you enter a word "
"with <guilabel>e</guilabel> instead of <guilabel>é</guilabel> it will still "
"count as right."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prezri naglase</guilabel>: s to možnostjo, če vnesete besedo z "
"<guilabel>e</guilabel> namesto <guilabel>é</guilabel>, bo še vedno štela kot "
"pravilna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Ignore capitalization</guilabel>: this option allows you to ignore "
"capitalization when you enter words."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prezri velike črke</guilabel>: ta možnost vam omogoča, da prezrete "
"velike začetnice, ko vnašate besede."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Images and Sound</guilabel> section: if you enable images they "
"will be displayed during the practice, if they are available. Same applies "
"to Sound."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek <guilabel>Slike in zvok</guilabel>: če omogočite slike, bodo "
"prikazane med vadbo, če bodo na voljo. Enako velja za zvok."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Allow images instead of words</guilabel>: if you enable this "
"option, it will allow an image to be used as the question during practice, "
"provided a translation is not set for that target language's word."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dovoli slike namesto besed</guilabel>: če omogočite to možnost, bo "
"dovolila uporabo slike kot vprašanje med vadbo, pod pogojem, da prevod ni "
"nastavljen za besedo tega ciljnega jezika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Blocking"
msgstr "Blokiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you plan to practice your vocabulary regularly, you should make sure that "
"the <emphasis>Blocking</emphasis> feature is enabled. Go to the "
"<guilabel>Blocking</guilabel> page and tick the check box that says "
"<guilabel>Blocking</guilabel>. Now you can even configure the interval in "
"which words that you answered correctly will be repeated."
msgstr ""
"Če nameravate redno vaditi svoje besedišče, se prepričajte, da je omogočena "
"funkcija <emphasis>Blokiranje</emphasis>. Pojdite na stran "
"<guilabel>Blokiranje</guilabel> in označite potrditveno polje "
"<guilabel>Blokiranje</guilabel>. Sedaj lahko celo konfigurirate interval, v "
"katerem se bodo ponavljale besede, na katere ste pravilno odgovorili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Blocking</emphasis> means that words will not be asked for some "
"period of time after the last practice. This period of time depends on how "
"well you know the word, so that words you don't know yet will be asked more "
"frequently."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Blokiranje</emphasis> pomeni, da besede nekaj časa po zadnji vadbi "
"ne bodo zahtevane. To obdobje je odvisno od tega, kako dobro poznate besedo, "
"tako da bodo besede, ki jih še ne poznate, vprašane pogosteje."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Blocking settings page"
msgstr "Stran z nastavitvami blokiranja"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thresholds"
msgstr "Pragi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thresholds are another way of limiting what you want to practice."
msgstr "Pragi so še en način omejevanja tega, kar želite vaditi."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thresholds settings page"
msgstr "Stran z nastavitvami pragov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can decide to practice only words that you know better or less well than "
"some confidence level. Or you can select only words that you have practiced "
"a certain number of times."
msgstr ""
"Lahko se odločite, da boste vadili samo besede, ki jih poznate bolje ali "
"manj dobro od določene stopnje zaupanja. Lahko pa izberete samo besede, ki "
"ste jih vadili določeno število krat."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specific Practice Settings"
msgstr "Posebne nastavitve vadbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configuration options for the practice with multiple choices can be changed "
"using the <guilabel>Specific</guilabel> settings page."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti konfiguracije za vadbo z več možnostmi lahko spremenite na strani z "
"nastavitvami <guilabel>Posebne</guilabel>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specific settings page"
msgstr "Stran s posebnimi nastavitvami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can select if the choices should be of the same type as well as the "
"number of choices."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko izberete, ali naj bodo izbire iste vrste, kot tudi število izbir."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Practice"
msgstr "Vadbe"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flash Cards"
msgstr "Flash kartice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After having activated the <guilabel>Flash Cards</guilabel> on the "
"<guilabel>Practice Mode</guilabel> section and having pressed on the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-start.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Start Practice..."
"</guiicon> icon in the toolbar the following screen shows up. The "
"<guilabel>Flash Cards</guilabel> Training Mode works just as if you would do "
"it with <quote>real</quote> flash cards. You imagine the result and should "
"you wish some help, you can press on the <guibutton>Hint</guibutton> button, "
"which will start to give you the result one letter at a time."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste aktivirali <guilabel>Flash kartice</guilabel> v razdelku "
"<guilabel>Način za vadbo</guilabel> in pritisnili na "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-start.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Začni vajo...</"
"guiicon> v orodni vrstici, se prikaže naslednji zaslon. Način usposabljanja "
"<guilabel>Flash kartice</guilabel> deluje tako, kot če bi to počeli s "
"<quote>pravimi</quote> flash karticami. Predstavljate si rezultat in če "
"potrebujete pomoč, lahko pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Namig</guibutton>, ki "
"vam bo začel prikazovati rezultat eno črko naenkrat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also decide to skip a word for now. When you press the "
"<guibutton>Answer Later</guibutton> button, the word will show up again at a "
"later time."
msgstr ""
"Lahko se tudi odločite, da za zdaj preskočite besedo. Ko pritisnete gumb "
"<guibutton>Odgovori pozneje</guibutton>, se bo beseda znova prikazala "
"pozneje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:312 index.docbook:334 index.docbook:351 index.docbook:368
#: index.docbook:379 index.docbook:390 index.docbook:408 index.docbook:419
#: index.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flash Cards Practice Mode"
msgstr "Flash kartice način vadbe"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word"
msgstr "Nova beseda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing on the <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button reveals the solution. "
"At this stage you then have to tell if you knew the answer."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton> se prikaže rešitev. Na "
"tej stopnji morate povedati, ali ste vedeli odgovor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you did not know it, press the <guibutton>I Did not Know it</guibutton> "
"button. If you did remember the answer, press the <guibutton>I Knew it</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če tega niste vedeli, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Nisem vedel</guibutton>. Če "
"ste se spomnili odgovora, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Vedel sem</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will take you to the next question."
msgstr "To vas bo pripeljalo do naslednjega vprašanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left hand side bottom of the screen you have 7 boxes that show how "
"good you know the vocabulary. These 7 boxes correspond to the blocking "
"levels set under <link linkend=\"blocking\"><guilabel>Blocking</guilabel></"
"link> page in the <guilabel>Configure Practice</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani spodaj zaslona imate 7 polj, ki prikazujejo, kako dobro "
"poznate besedišče. Teh 7 polj ustreza stopnjam blokiranja, nastavljenim na "
"strani <link linkend=\"blocking\"><guilabel>Blokiranje</guilabel></link> v "
"pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Konfiguriraj vadbo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Instead of pressing the <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button, you can also "
"use the &Space; key."
msgstr ""
"Namesto da pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton>, lahko uporabite "
"tudi tipko &Space;."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - confirmation"
msgstr "Nova beseda - potrditev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341 index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can stop practicing anytime by pressing on the <guibutton>Stop Practice</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Vadbo lahko kadar koli prekinete s pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Prenehaj z "
"vadbo</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mixed Letters"
msgstr "Mešane črke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mixed Letters is a training method that provides you with an immediate help: "
"all letters that are part of the solution are shown mixed up:"
msgstr ""
"Mešane črke je metoda usposabljanja, ki vam nudi takojšnjo pomoč: vse črke, "
"ki so del rešitve, so prikazane pomešane:"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - mixed letters"
msgstr "Nova beseda - mešane črke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Should you wish some help, you can press on the <guibutton>Hint</guibutton> "
"button, which will give you the solution one letter at a time. Of course you "
"can also decide to <guibutton>Answer Later</guibutton> by pressing on that "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Če potrebujete pomoč, lahko pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Namig</guibutton>, ki "
"vam bo ponudil rešitev črko za črko. Seveda se lahko odločite tudi za "
"<guibutton>Odgovori pozneje</guibutton> s pritiskom na ta gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To give the answer type it in the blank field below the mixed letters and "
"press the &Enter; key or <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dati odgovor, ga vnesite v prazno polje pod mešanimi črkami in "
"pritisnite &Enter; tipko ali gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your answer was correct &parley; will tell you so and you can press "
"&Enter; again or press on the <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button to go "
"ahead with the next question."
msgstr ""
"Če je bil vaš odgovor pravilen &parley; vam bo to povedal in lahko "
"pritisnete &Enter; ponovno ali pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</"
"guibutton>, da nadaljujete z naslednjim vprašanjem."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - mixed letters right"
msgstr "Nova beseda - mešane črke desno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Should you enter a wrong answer, you will be told to <emphasis>try again</"
"emphasis>:"
msgstr ""
"Če vnesete napačen odgovor, boste pozvani, da <emphasis>poskusite znova</"
"emphasis>:"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - wrong answer, try again"
msgstr "Nova beseda - napačen odgovor, poskusite znova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you don't know the answer, just press on the <guibutton>Continue</"
"guibutton> button a second time. Then the following comes up and you are "
"shown the solution. Go ahead with <guibutton>Continue</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Če ne poznate odgovora, drugič pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</"
"guibutton>. Nato se pojavi naslednje in prikazana vam je rešitev. Nadaljujte "
"z <guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - wrong answer, show the right answer"
msgstr "Nova beseda - napačen odgovor, pokaži pravi odgovor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:397 index.docbook:437 index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can overrule how your answer is counted. See <link linkend=\"practice-"
"overview\">Practice Overview</link>."
msgstr ""
"Način štetja vašega odgovora lahko preglasite. Glejte <link linkend="
"\"practice-overview\">Pregled vadbe</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:401
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiple Choice"
msgstr "Več možnosti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic selection of the possible answers"
msgstr "Samodejna izbira možnih odgovorov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <guilabel>Multiple Choice</guilabel> mode you are shown a number of "
"potential answers, of which only one is correct. By pressing on the "
"<guibutton>Hint</guibutton> button, &parley; excludes one of the wrong "
"answers so that your choice gets more and more restricted with each further "
"press on <guibutton>Hint</guibutton>. The answer is revealed when only one "
"option is left and the question is counted as wrong. Of course you may also "
"choose the <guibutton>Answer Later</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"V načinu <guilabel>Multiple Choice</guilabel> se vam prikaže več možnih "
"odgovorov, od katerih je le eden pravilen. S pritiskom na gumb "
"<guibutton>Namig</guibutton>, &parley; izključi enega od napačnih odgovorov, "
"tako da je vaša izbira vedno bolj omejena z vsakim nadaljnjim pritiskom na "
"<guibutton>Namig</guibutton>. Odgovor se razkrije, ko ostane samo ena "
"možnost in se vprašanje šteje kot napačno. Seveda lahko izberete tudi gumb "
"<guibutton>Odgovori pozneje</guibutton>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - Multiple Choice mode"
msgstr "Nova beseda - način več izbir"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you made your choice by clicking on what you believe to be correct or "
"type the number in front of the choice, &parley; shows up with the screen "
"below if the answer was right. Go ahead with the next question by pressing "
"on the <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ko se odločite tako, da kliknete tisto, kar menite, da je pravilno, ali "
"vnesete številko pred izbiro, &parley; se prikaže s spodnjim zaslonom, če je "
"bil odgovor pravilen. Nadaljujte z naslednjim vprašanjem s pritiskom na gumb "
"<guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - Multiple Choice, right answer"
msgstr "Nova beseda - več možnosti, pravi odgovor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your answer instead was wrong, the correct answer will be shown in green "
"and the wrong one in red. Also here you go ahead by pressing on the "
"<guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če je bil vaš odgovor napačen, bo pravilen odgovor prikazan zeleno, napačen "
"pa rdeče. Tudi tukaj nadaljujete s pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - Multiple Choice, wrong answer"
msgstr "Nova beseda - več možnosti, napačen odgovor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wish to stop practice, just press on the <guibutton>Stop Practice</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prekiniti vadbo, preprosto pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Prenehaj "
"vajo</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "With yes/no answers"
msgstr "Z odgovori da/ne"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Normally &parley; automatically proposes one correct and several wrong "
"answers in Multiple Choice mode. For some exercises instead you will have "
"preset answers like yes/no or similar. And for these you have to configure "
"the practice by selecting the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"practice-setup.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> <link linkend=\"advanced-practice-configuration"
"\"><guiicon>Configure Practice...</guiicon></link> icon in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Običajno &parley; samodejno predlaga enega pravilnega in več napačnih "
"odgovorov v načinu več izbir. Za nekatere vaje boste namesto tega imeli "
"prednastavljene odgovore, kot je da/ne ali podobno. In za te morate "
"konfigurirati vadbo tako, da izberete "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-setup.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <link linkend=\"advanced-"
"practice-configuration\"><guiicon>Konfiguriraj vadbo...</guiicon></link> "
"ikono v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>Specific</guilabel> page and you will get something "
"very similar to the following screenshot:"
msgstr ""
"Izberite stran <guilabel>Specific</guilabel> in dobili boste nekaj zelo "
"podobnega naslednjemu posnetku zaslona:"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specific page"
msgstr "Določena stran"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have just <emphasis>two choices</emphasis> like <emphasis>yes/no</"
"emphasis> in the section <guilabel>Multiple Choice</guilabel> set the "
"<guilabel>Number of choices:</guilabel> to <parameter>2</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"Če imate samo <emphasis>dve možnosti</emphasis>, kot je <emphasis>da/ne</"
"emphasis> v razdelku <guilabel>Več možnosti</guilabel>, nastavite "
"<guilabel>Število možnosti:</guilabel> na <parameter>2</parameter>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid "Written"
msgstr "Napisano"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you select the option <guilabel>Written</guilabel> to do your practice "
"you are supposed to type in the solution. You can use the <guibutton>Hint</"
"guibutton> button, which will start to give you the result one letter at a "
"time. Of course you can also decide to <guibutton>Answer Later</guibutton> "
"by pressing on that button."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete možnost <guilabel>Pisno</guilabel> za vajo, morate vnesti "
"rešitev. Uporabite lahko gumb <guibutton>Namig</guibutton>, ki vam bo začel "
"prikazovati rezultat črko za črko. Seveda se lahko odločite tudi za "
"<guibutton>Odgovori pozneje</guibutton> s pritiskom na ta gumb."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:471 index.docbook:482 index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Written Practice Mode"
msgstr "Način pisne vaje"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - Written Practice Mode"
msgstr "Nova beseda - Način pisne vaje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have entered the solution, press on the <guibutton>Continue</"
"guibutton> button and &parley; will show whether your answer was correct. Go "
"ahead by pressing on <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> again."
msgstr ""
"Ko vnesete rešitev, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton> in "
"&parley; bo pokazalo, ali je bil vaš odgovor pravilen. Nadaljujte s ponovnim "
"pritiskom na <guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - Written Practice Mode, right answer"
msgstr "Nova beseda - način pisne vaje, pravi odgovor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Should you give a wrong answer, you may try again several times to find the "
"right answer. If you don't try again, and just press on the "
"<guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button, the solution will be shown."
msgstr ""
"Če podate napačen odgovor, lahko večkrat poskusite najti pravi odgovor. Če "
"ne poskusite znova in samo pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton>, "
"bo prikazana rešitev."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - Written Practice Mode, wrong answer"
msgstr "Nova beseda - Način pisne vaje, napačen odgovor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go ahead practicing by pressing on <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> or stop "
"by pressing on the button <guibutton>Stop Practice</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Nadaljujte z vadbo s pritiskom na <guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton> ali "
"ustavite s pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Prenehaj z vadbo</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reset Practice to Initial State"
msgstr "Ponastavi vadbo na začetno stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reset all your practice scores (remove the confidence levels) to the "
"initial state. You can reset your confidence levels for individual units "
"from within the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"practice-start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Practice Overview</guiicon> icon in the toolbar and by clicking "
"with &RMB; on the unit to reset and choosing <guimenuitem>Remove confidence "
"levels from this unit</guimenuitem> or by choosing <guimenuitem>Remove "
"confidence levels from this unit and all sub-units</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Vse rezultate vadbe lahko ponastavite (odstranite stopnje zaupanja) na "
"začetno stanje. Stopnje zaupanja za posamezne enote lahko ponastavite v "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-start.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Pregled vadbe</"
"guiicon> v orodni vrstici in s klikom z &RMB; na enoti za ponastavitev in "
"izbiro <guimenuitem>Odstrani stopnje zaupanja iz te enote</guimenuitem> ali "
"tako, da izberete <guimenuitem>Odstrani stopnje zaupanja iz te enote in vseh "
"podenot</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Summary After Practice</title>"
msgstr "<title>Povzetek po vaji</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The summary shows up when you finish a learning session. In the big bar on "
"the top it shows you how well you did."
msgstr ""
"Povzetek se prikaže, ko končate učno sejo. V veliki vrstici na vrhu je "
"prikazano, kako dobro ste se odrezali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below is a table with all the words you practiced, together with the "
"mistakes you made."
msgstr ""
"Spodaj je tabela z vsemi besedami, ki ste jih vadili, skupaj z napakami, ki "
"ste jih naredili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The words with the most mistakes are on top so you can easily see what you "
"do not know yet."
msgstr ""
"Besede z največ napakami so na vrhu, tako da lahko preprosto vidite, česar "
"še ne poznate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"export.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Export Results...</guiicon> icon in the toolbar or use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Practice</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export Results...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to export practice results as &HTML; or "
"OpenDocument text file (<literal role=\"extension\">.odt</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite ikono <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-export.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Izvozi rezultate ...</guiicon> v orodni vrstici ali uporabite "
"menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Vaja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvozi "
"rezultate ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> za izvoz rezultatov vaje kot &HTML; "
"ali besedilno datoteko OpenDocument (<literal role=\"extension\">.odt</"
"literal>)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Summary After Practice</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Povzetek po vadbi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "<caption>Summary After Practice</caption>"
msgstr "<caption>Povzetek po vadbi</caption>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grammar Practice Modes"
msgstr "Načini vadbe slovnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With &parley; you can also learn specific grammar structures, such as the "
"gender of nouns, the comparison forms of adjectives and the conjugation of "
"verbs. Let's look at some examples."
msgstr ""
"Z &parley; naučite se lahko tudi posebnih slovničnih struktur, kot so spol "
"samostalnikov, primerjalne oblike pridevnikov in spregatev glagolov. "
"Poglejmo si nekaj primerov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid "Articles and Gender of Nouns"
msgstr "Členi in rod samostalnikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the practice mode <guilabel>Gender of Nouns</guilabel> is activated, "
"press on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-"
"start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Start Practice...</guiicon> icon in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Ko je aktiviran vadbeni način <guilabel>Spol samostalnikov</guilabel>, "
"pritisnite <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-"
"start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Začni vajo...</guiicon> ikona v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the case below we use German as language to learn and so you have three "
"genders to choose from: masculine, feminine and neuter. By pressing on "
"<guibutton>Hint</guibutton> one of the wrong answers gets excluded. Of "
"course you can also decide to <guibutton>Answer Later</guibutton> by "
"pressing on that button."
msgstr ""
"V spodnjem primeru uporabljamo nemščino kot jezik za učenje, tako da lahko "
"izbirate med tremi spoli: moškim, ženskim in srednjim. S pritiskom na "
"<guibutton>Namig</guibutton> je eden od napačnih odgovorov izključen. Seveda "
"se lahko odločite tudi za <guibutton>Odgovori pozneje</guibutton> s "
"pritiskom na ta gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should enter the articles for the language in the Editor to see the "
"articles instead of the grammatical gender terms. Also note that this only "
"works, if the gender of the words has been set up properly. See <link "
"linkend=\"word-types\">Word Types</link> for more information how to change "
"the word type to the right gender."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti članke namesto slovničnih spolnih izrazov, morate v "
"urejevalnik vnesti člene za jezik. Upoštevajte tudi, da to deluje le, če je "
"bil spol besed pravilno nastavljen. Glejte <link linkend=\"word-types"
"\">Besedne vrste</link> za več informacij, kako spremeniti besedno vrsto v "
"pravi spol."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:555 index.docbook:566 index.docbook:577
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gender of Nouns Practice Mode"
msgstr "Način vadbe spola samostalnikov"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - Gender of Nouns Practice Mode"
msgstr "Nova beseda - Način vadbe spola samostalnikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you give the correct answer the following is shown and you go ahead "
"practicing by pressing on the <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ko podate pravilen odgovor, se prikaže naslednje in nadaljujete z vadbo s "
"pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - Gender of Nouns, right answer"
msgstr "Nova beseda - Rod samostalnikov, pravi odgovor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Should you give the wrong answer the following is shown and you go ahead "
"practicing by pressing on the <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če podate napačen odgovor, se prikaže naslednje in nadaljujete z vadbo s "
"pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - Gender of Nouns, wrong answer"
msgstr "Nova beseda - Rod samostalnikov, napačen odgovor"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comparison Forms of Adjectives and Adverbs"
msgstr "Primerjalne oblike pridevnikov in prislovov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the <guilabel>Practice Mode</guilabel> section, select "
"<guilabel>Comparison Forms</guilabel> and then press on the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-start.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Start Practice..."
"</guiicon> icon in the toolbar to go ahead."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Način za vadbo</guilabel> izberite <guilabel>Obrazci za "
"primerjavo</guilabel> in nato pritisnite "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-start.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\" /></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Začni vajo...</"
"guiicon> ikono v orodni vrstici, da nadaljujete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This only works when the conjugation forms of the word have been entered in "
"the vocabulary collection. See <link linkend=\"entering-comparison-forms"
"\">Entering Comparison Forms</link>."
msgstr ""
"To deluje le, če so spregatvene oblike besede vnesene v zbirko besedišča. "
"Glejte <link linkend=\"entering-comparison-forms\">Vnos obrazcev za "
"primerjavo</link>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid "<caption>Comparison Forms Practice Mode</caption>"
msgstr "<caption>Način za vadbo primerjalnih obrazcev</caption>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The exercise requires you to enter the comparison forms for the term shown. "
"In this case the translation of the English word <emphasis>old</emphasis> to "
"German. The German language has three forms: <emphasis>absolute, "
"comparative</emphasis> and <emphasis>superlative</emphasis>. To go on with "
"the exercise just press on the <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Vaja zahteva, da vnesete primerjalne obrazce za prikazan izraz. V tem "
"primeru prevod angleške besede <emphasis>old</emphasis> v nemščino. Nemški "
"jezik ima tri oblike: <emphasis>absolutno, primerjalno</emphasis> in "
"<emphasis>superlativno</emphasis>. Za nadaljevanje vaje samo pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Comparison Forms Practice Mode</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Način za vadbo primerjalnih obrazcev</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "New word - comparison right"
msgstr "Nova beseda - primerjava prav"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid "Conjugations"
msgstr "Spregatve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To practice conjugations choose the <guilabel>Conjugations</guilabel> mode "
"and the tenses you wish to exercise."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vaditi spregatve, izberite način <guilabel>Spregatve</guilabel> in "
"čase, ki jih želite vaditi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the document the conjugation forms of the words have to be entered in "
"order to allow this practice mode to work. See <link linkend=\"entering-"
"inflection-forms\">Entering Inflection Forms</link>."
msgstr ""
"V dokument je treba vnesti spregatvene oblike besed, da lahko ta način vadbe "
"deluje. Glejte <link linkend=\"entering-inflection-forms\">Vnos pregibnih "
"oblik</link>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:628
#, no-c-format
msgid "<caption>Conjugations Practice Mode</caption>"
msgstr "<caption>Način za vadbo spregatev</caption>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then press on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"practice-start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Start Practice...</guiicon> icon in the toolbar. You are required "
"to enter the correct conjugation forms according to the tense shown. To go "
"ahead press on the <guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Nato v orodno vrstico. Vnesti morate pravilne oblike spregatve glede na "
"prikazani čas. Za nadaljevanje pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Conjugations Practice Mode</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Način za vadbo spregatev</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid "Conjugation Practice"
msgstr "Vadba spregatev"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vocabulary Editing"
msgstr "Urejanje besedišča"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:649 index.docbook:830 index.docbook:927 index.docbook:970
#: index.docbook:997 index.docbook:1019 index.docbook:1039 index.docbook:1050
#: index.docbook:1126 index.docbook:1157 index.docbook:1177 index.docbook:1188
#: index.docbook:1208 index.docbook:1219 index.docbook:1236 index.docbook:1258
#: index.docbook:1269 index.docbook:1280 index.docbook:1291 index.docbook:1302
#: index.docbook:1378 index.docbook:1389 index.docbook:1400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor window"
msgstr "Okno urejevalnika"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing the practices"
msgstr "Urejanje vadb"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setup"
msgstr "Nastavljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before you start using a vocabulary collection or create your own it is "
"helpful to understand the different elements in &parley; and configure them "
"accordingly. The next sections will guide you step by step through this "
"process. There are several locations in &parley; for settings:"
msgstr ""
"Preden začnete uporabljati zbirko besedišča ali ustvarite svojo lastno, je "
"koristno razumeti različne elemente v &parley; in jih ustrezno "
"konfigurirajte. Naslednji razdelki vas bodo korak za korakom vodili skozi ta "
"postopek. Obstaja več lokacij v &parley; za nastavitve:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Properties...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> This is the place for the <guilabel>General "
"Document Properties</guilabel>, meaning some information about your "
"vocabulary collection and yourself."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lastnosti...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> To je mesto za <guilabel>Splošne lastnosti "
"dokumenta</guilabel>, kar pomeni nekaj informacij o vaši zbirki besedišča in "
"sebe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Languages...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> Opens the <guilabel>Edit Languages</guilabel> dialog, where you "
"will find the settings around the languages you use."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Jeziki ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> Odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Urejanje jezikov</guilabel>, kjer "
"boste našli nastavitve za jezike, ki jih uporabljate ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Practice</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Practice...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> Here are settings how you practice your "
"vocabulary. Depending on what you want to do during the specific learning "
"session you change them on the fly."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Vaja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj vajo ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> Tukaj so nastavitve, kako vadite svoje besedišče. "
"Odvisno od tega, kaj želite početi med določeno učno sejo, jih spreminjate "
"sproti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &parley;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> For more general and display settings."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&parley;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> Za bolj splošne in prikazne "
"nastavitve."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid "About the Collection"
msgstr "O zbirki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entering meta data like a title and your contact info is relevant if you "
"plan to make your collection available for other people. Use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Properties...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to edit the data."
msgstr ""
"Vnos metapodatkov, kot sta naslov in vaši kontaktni podatki, je ustrezen, če "
"nameravate svojo zbirko dati na voljo drugim ljudem. Za urejanje podatkov "
"uporabite element menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties for <quote>filename.kvtml</quote> dialog"
msgstr "Lastnosti za pogovorno okno <quote>filename.kvtml</quote>"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:680
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing the properties"
msgstr "Urejanje lastnosti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vocabulary Columns"
msgstr "Stolpci besedišča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on what your learning sessions are going to be about it can be "
"relevant to have further Vocabulary Columns show up in your edit section. To "
"choose these columns select the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Vocabulary Columns...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. "
"There you can determine if the columns for <emphasis>Pronunciation, Word "
"Type, Synonym, Antonym, Example, Comment</emphasis> and/or "
"<emphasis>Paraphrase</emphasis> are to be shown."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od tega, o čem bodo govorile vaše učne ure, je lahko pomembno, da se "
"v razdelku za urejanje prikažejo dodatni stolpci besedišča. Če želite "
"izbrati te stolpce, izberite menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stolpci besedišča...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Tam "
"lahko določite, ali naj bodo prikazani stolpci za <emphasis>Izgovorjava, "
"Besedna vrsta, Sinonim, Protipomenka, Primer, Komentar</emphasis> in/ali "
"<emphasis>Parafraza</emphasis>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:691 index.docbook:1247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vocabulary Columns dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Stolpci besedišča"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting the columns"
msgstr "Nastavitev stolpcev"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid "Languages and Grammar"
msgstr "Jeziki in slovnica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set up some grammar details to let &parley; help you. Use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Languages...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item to pull up a grammar."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite nekaj slovničnih podrobnosti, da bo &parley; ti pomagam. Uporabite "
"menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Jeziki..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da prikažete slovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:704
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Articles in English are simply <guilabel>the</guilabel> which is the "
"definite article and <guilabel>a</guilabel> as indefinite article. Most "
"other languages have more articles which can be filled in at the "
"<guilabel>Articles</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Členki v angleščini so preprosto <guilabel>the</guilabel>, ki je določni "
"člen, in <guilabel>a</guilabel> kot nedoločni člen. Večina drugih jezikov "
"ima več členov, ki jih lahko izpolnite na zavihku <guilabel>Članki</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For conjugations the personal pronouns should be filled out. Most languages "
"do not have different conjugation forms for he/she/it, in that case, you "
"should <emphasis>not</emphasis> check <guilabel>Male/female have different "
"conjugations</guilabel>! Simply enter the pronouns for all three forms."
msgstr ""
"Za spregatve je treba izpolniti osebne zaimke. Večina jezikov nima različnih "
"spregatvenih oblik za on/ona/to, v tem primeru <emphasis>ne</emphasis> "
"označite <guilabel>Moški/ženska imata različne spregatve</guilabel>! "
"Preprosto vnesite zaimke za vse tri oblike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Personal Pronouns in English"
msgstr "Osebni zaimki v angleščini"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:716
#, no-c-format
msgid "Singular"
msgstr "Ednina"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plural"
msgstr "Množina"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:720
#, no-c-format
msgid "1st Person"
msgstr "1. oseba"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>I</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>Jaz</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>we</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>mi</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid "2nd Person"
msgstr "2. oseba"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:726 index.docbook:727
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>you</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>vi</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid "3rd Person"
msgstr "3. oseba"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid "he/she/it"
msgstr "on/ona/ono"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid "they"
msgstr "oni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Tenses</guilabel> tab: Depending on the language, you can enter "
"the right tenses which you later want to learn how to conjugate. Examples "
"are: Simple Present, Simple Past, Future I, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Časi</guilabel>: Odvisno od jezika lahko vnesete prave "
"čase, ki se jih želite pozneje naučiti spregati. Primeri so: preprosta "
"sedanjost, preprosta preteklost, prihodnost, &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Btw. by pressing on the <guibutton>Add Language</guibutton> button you can "
"add an additional language to your collection."
msgstr ""
"Mimogrede pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Dodaj jezik</guibutton> lahko svoji "
"zbirki dodate dodaten jezik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid "Let's Have a Closer Look at Spanish"
msgstr "Oglejmo si španščino pobližje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:746
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab the basic language settings, like "
"here:"
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> osnovne jezikovne nastavitve, kot je "
"tukaj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Language:</guilabel> Spanish"
msgstr "<guilabel>Jezik:</guilabel> španščina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:751
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Name:</guilabel> Spanish"
msgstr "<guilabel>Ime:</guilabel> španščina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Keyboard layout:</guilabel> us (for English)"
msgstr "<guilabel>Razporeditev tipkovnice:</guilabel> us (za angleščino)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can leave <guilabel>Keyboard layout:</guilabel> empty if you are not "
"sure about what you are using. &parley; will then simply take the standard "
"layout of your computer."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razporeditev tipkovnice:</guilabel> lahko pustite prazno, če niste "
"prepričani, kaj uporabljate. &parley; bo nato preprosto prevzel standardno "
"postavitev vašega računalnika."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:759 index.docbook:770 index.docbook:781 index.docbook:792
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Language dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za urejanje jezika"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing a language"
msgstr "Urejanje jezika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's have a look at the <guilabel>Articles</guilabel> tab: Spanish knows "
"only male and female nouns, therefore the field <guilabel>Neutral:</"
"guilabel> remains empty."
msgstr ""
"Oglejmo si zavihek <guilabel>Členi</guilabel>: španščina pozna samo moške in "
"ženske samostalnike, zato polje <guilabel>Nevtralno:</guilabel> ostane "
"prazno."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid "Articles tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Členi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Spanish <guilabel>Personal Pronouns</guilabel> tab have multiple forms for "
"3rd person singular and 1st, 2nd and 3rd person plural. To remain "
"consistent, the possibilities should be entered with a <guilabel>/</"
"guilabel> between the two forms."
msgstr ""
"Špansko zavihek <guilabel>Osebni zaimki</guilabel> ima več oblik za 3. osebo "
"ednine ter 1., 2. in 3. osebo množine. Da ostanete dosledni, je treba "
"možnosti vnesti z <guilabel>/</guilabel> med oba obrazca."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid "Personal Pronouns tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Osebni zaimki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Under <guilabel>Tenses</guilabel> tab you will find the various tenses that "
"are available for a verb form. You can add to the tenses that are already "
"there by pressing the buttons <guibutton>New...</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>Modify...</guibutton> or in case something does not actually "
"exist simply <guibutton>Delete</guibutton> the tense after having it "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Pod zavihkom <guilabel>Časi</guilabel> boste našli različne čase, ki so na "
"voljo za glagolsko obliko. Čase, ki so že tam, lahko dodate tako, da "
"pritisnete gumbe <guibutton>Novo...</guibutton>, <guibutton>Spremeni...</"
"guibutton> ali v primeru, da nekaj dejansko ne obstaja preprosto "
"<guibutton>Izbriši </guibutton> čas, potem ko ste ga izbrali."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:795
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tenses tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Časi"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:802
#, no-c-format
msgid "Units"
msgstr "Enote"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left you have a list of units. If you started a new collection, this "
"list might be empty except for one unit that was created by default for you."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani imate seznam enot. Če ste začeli novo zbirko, bo ta seznam "
"morda prazen, razen ene enote, ki je bila privzeto ustvarjena za vas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you cannot see the list of units, you might have to enable it in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Units</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> check box."
msgstr ""
"Če ne vidite seznama enot, ga boste morda morali omogočiti v potrditvenem "
"polju <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enote</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The check boxes in front of the unit name show which units are currently "
"included in your practice. The number next to it is the number of words in "
"the unit."
msgstr ""
"Potrditvena polja pred imenom enote prikazujejo, katere enote so trenutno "
"vključene v vašo vadbo. Številka zraven je število besed v enoti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Unit"
msgstr "Nova enota"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:815
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select where this unit belongs to, for example the collection <guilabel>My "
"Spanish Lessons</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, kam ta enota spada, na primer v zbirko <guilabel>Moje lekcije "
"španščine</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select <guilabel>New Unit</guilabel> item using one of the following "
"ways:"
msgstr ""
"Element <guilabel>Nova enota</guilabel> lahko izberete na enega od "
"naslednjih načinov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:822
#, no-c-format
msgid "&GUI; icon: select the <guiicon>New Unit</guiicon> icon in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"&GUI; ikona: v orodni vrstici izberite ikono <guiicon>Nova enota</guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Menu item: select <menuchoice><guimenu>Unit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Unit</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Element menija: izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Enota</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Nova enota</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Context menu: click with the &RMB; on the collection and select "
"<guimenuitem>New Unit</guimenuitem> item."
msgstr ""
"Kontekstni meni: kliknite z &RMB; v zbirki in izberite element "
"<guimenuitem>Nova enota</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collection: My Spanish Lessons"
msgstr "Zbirka: Moje lekcije španščine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please make sure to select the right point in the tree structure of units "
"before selecting <guiicon>New Unit</guiicon> icon in the toolbar. In our "
"case, wanting a <emphasis>Sub-Unit</emphasis> of <guilabel>Collection: My "
"Spanish Lessons</guilabel> it is exactly that one that needs to be selected "
"before going ahead with <guiicon>New Unit</guiicon>."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da ste izbrali pravo točko v drevesni strukturi enot, preden "
"v orodni vrstici izberete ikono <guiicon>Nova enota</guiicon>. V našem "
"primeru, ko želimo <emphasis>Podenoto</emphasis> <guilabel>Zbirke: Moje "
"lekcije španščine</guilabel>, je treba točno to izbrati, preden nadaljujemo "
"z <guiicon>Novo enoto</guiicon>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:842
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving, Renaming and Deleting Units"
msgstr "Premikanje, preimenovanje in brisanje enot"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the name of a unit, double click it, or click with the &RMB; on "
"the unit and choose <guimenuitem>Rename Unit</guimenuitem>. You can also "
"delete it this way (but you'll lose its contents also then)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti ime enote, jo dvokliknite ali kliknite z &RMB; na enoti "
"in izberite <guimenuitem>Preimenuj enoto</guimenuitem>. Lahko ga tudi "
"izbrišete na ta način (vendar boste takrat izgubili tudi njegovo vsebino)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you don't like the arrangement of units, you can move a unit with the "
"mouse. You can drag it onto another unit, then it will become a child of "
"that unit."
msgstr ""
"Če vam razporeditev enot ni všeč, lahko enoto premikate z miško. Lahko ga "
"povlečete na drugo enoto, potem bo postal podrejeni element te enote."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid "Splitting a Unit"
msgstr "Razdelitev enote"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:853
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your units grow too big, you can choose to split them up to make learning "
"easier in small units. 20 words for a unit is probably a good size. Click "
"with the &RMB; on a unit, or use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Unit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Split Unit into Smaller Units</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item and the unit will be separated into child units. You can choose to "
"randomize the words that are put into the new units before assigning them, "
"or to keep them in order."
msgstr ""
"Če vaše enote postanejo prevelike, jih lahko razdelite, da olajšate učenje v "
"majhnih enotah. 20 besed za enoto je verjetno dobra velikost. Kliknite z "
"&RMB; na enoti ali uporabite menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Enota</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razdeli enoto na manjše enote</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in enota bo ločena na podrejene enote. Izberete lahko naključno "
"razporejanje besed, ki so vstavljene v nove enote, preden jih dodelite, ali "
"pa jih ohranite v vrstnem redu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is Shown in the Table"
msgstr "Kaj je prikazano v tabeli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:859
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&parley; shows always the words of the unit that you have currently "
"selected. You can enable to see the words in sub-units contained in this "
"unit also. Use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Unit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Entries from Child Units</guimenuitem></menuchoice> check box to enable "
"this. That way, you can browse all words by selecting the document unit at "
"the very top."
msgstr ""
"&parley; vedno prikazuje besede enote, ki ste jo trenutno izbrali. Omogočite "
"lahko tudi ogled besed v podenotah, ki jih vsebuje ta enota. Uporabite "
"potrditveno polje <menuchoice><guimenu>Enota</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži "
"vnose iz podrejenih enot</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da to omogočite. Tako "
"lahko brskate po vseh besedah z izbiro enote dokumenta čisto na vrhu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid "Word Types"
msgstr "Besedne vrste"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&parley; lets you associate word types with the words. Word types are for "
"example: Nouns, Verbs, Adjectives and Adverbs."
msgstr ""
"&parley; vam omogoča povezovanje besednih vrst z besedami. Besedne vrste so "
"na primer: samostalniki, glagoli, pridevniki in prislovi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to work with word types, enable the word type tool with the check "
"box: <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Word Types</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Za delo z besednimi vrstami omogočite orodje za besedne vrste s potrditvenim "
"poljem: <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Besedne vrste</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can categorize the word types just like units."
msgstr "Besedne vrste lahko kategorizirate tako kot enote."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to see all words of a certain type - &eg; all nouns, simply "
"select the noun category, and you will see only nouns in the table."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti vse besede določene vrste - &eg; vsi samostalniki, "
"preprosto izberite kategorijo samostalnikov in v tabeli boste videli samo "
"samostalnike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The easiest way to set the word type, is to drag and drop a word onto its "
"type. You can even do this with multiple words at the same time."
msgstr ""
"Besedno vrsto najlažje nastavite tako, da besedo povlečete in spustite na "
"njeno vrsto. To lahko storite celo z več besedami hkrati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding New Vocabulary"
msgstr "Dodajanje novega besedišča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:887
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Add New Entry</"
"guiicon> icon in the toolbar to add new words. You can start typing the word "
"in the first language right away. After entering the first word, press &Tab; "
"key to go to the next language."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite ikono <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-"
"add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Dodaj "
"nov vnos</guiicon> v orodni vrstici, da dodate nove besede. Takoj lahko "
"začnete vnašati besedo v prvem jeziku. Po vnosu prve besede pritisnite &Tab; "
"tipko za prehod na naslednji jezik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:891
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Words"
msgstr "Urejanje besed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:893
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to replace a word, select its entry and start typing. To change "
"the word instead, double click the entry and you can change the contents of "
"the cell without losing the old word."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zamenjati besedo, izberite njen vnos in začnite tipkati. Če želite "
"spremeniti besedo, dvokliknite vnos in lahko spremenite vsebino celice, ne "
"da bi izgubili staro besedo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press &Tab; key to go to the next word while staying in editing mode. "
"&Enter; key leaves this mode. You can use the arrow keys to move around."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite &Tab; tipko za prehod na naslednjo besedo, medtem ko ostanete v "
"načinu za urejanje. &Enter; tipka zapusti ta način. Za premikanje lahko "
"uporabljate puščične tipke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synonyms"
msgstr "Sopomenke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Synonyms are hard to set up and do not always work really well. Here is how "
"you set them up in any case:"
msgstr ""
"Sinonime je težko nastaviti in ne delujejo vedno dobro. V vsakem primeru jih "
"nastavite tako:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:907
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Synonyms</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> check box to see the synonyms tool."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled orodja za sinonime uporabite potrditveno polje "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sinonimi</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select first word (A) you want to make synonyms, then click on the second "
"word (B)."
msgstr ""
"Izberite prvo besedo (A), za katero želite narediti sinonime, nato kliknite "
"drugo besedo (B)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:911
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The button in the synonym tool changes it's text to <guibutton>A and B are "
"Synonyms</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Gumb v orodju za sinonime spremeni svoje besedilo v <guibutton>A in B sta "
"sinonima</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The words will now be shown as connected in the synonym tool and can be "
"recognized as synonyms in the practice."
msgstr ""
"Besede bodo zdaj v orodju za sinonime prikazane kot povezane in jih bo v "
"vadbi mogoče prepoznati kot sinonime."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:918
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Images"
msgstr "Dodajanje slik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First show the image tool by selecting the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Image</guimenuitem></menuchoice> check box. This will "
"show up the <guilabel>Image</guilabel> section on the right hand side of the "
"&parley; screen."
msgstr ""
"Najprej pokažite slikovno orodje tako, da izberete potrditveno polje "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Slika</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. To bo prikazalo razdelek <guilabel>Slika</guilabel> na desni "
"strani &parley; zaslon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add an image to a word make sure the word is highlighted. In the "
"<guilabel>Image</guilabel> section on the right hand side press on the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"folder-black.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Folder</guiicon> "
"icon and choose the picture you wish to associate. On selecting an image for "
"a pair of translations, the bottom right corners of the cells of both the "
"words would be marked with a blue flag. If you want this way, do the same "
"with the other word of the couple. Hovering over this flag with the mouse "
"cursor shows the name and path of the image file."
msgstr ""
"Če želite besedi dodati sliko, se prepričajte, da je beseda označena. V "
"razdelku <guilabel>Slika</guilabel> na desni strani pritisnite "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"folder-black.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject > ikono <guiicon>Mapa</"
"guiicon> in izberite sliko, ki jo želite povezati. Pri izbiri slike za par "
"prevodov bi bili spodnji desni koti celic obeh besed označeni z modro "
"zastavico. Če želite tako, storite enako z drugo besedo para. Če s kazalcem "
"miške premaknete nad to zastavico, se prikažeta ime in pot do slikovne "
"datoteke."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:930
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a image"
msgstr "Dodajanje slike"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:961
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Sound"
msgstr "Dodajanje zvoka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:963
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First show the sound tool by selecting the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sound</guimenuitem></menuchoice> check box. This will "
"show up the <guilabel>Sound</guilabel> section on the right hand side of the "
"&parley; screen."
msgstr ""
"Najprej pokažite zvočno orodje tako, da izberete potrditveno polje "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zvok</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. To bo prikazalo razdelek <guilabel>Zvok</guilabel> na desni "
"strani &parley; zaslon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a sound to a word make sure the word is highlighted. In the "
"<guilabel>Sound</guilabel> section on the right hand side press on the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"folder-black.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Folder</guiicon> "
"icon and choose the sound you wish to associate. On selecting a sound file "
"for a word, the top right corner of the cell of that word would be marked "
"with a red flag. If you want this way, do the same with the other word of "
"the couple. Hovering over this flag with the mouse cursor shows the name and "
"path of the sound file."
msgstr ""
"Če želite besedi dodati zvok, se prepričajte, da je beseda označena. V "
"razdelku <guilabel>Zvok</guilabel> na desni strani pritisnite "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"folder-black.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject > ikona <guiicon>Mapa</"
"guiicon> in izberite zvok, ki ga želite povezati. Pri izbiri zvočne datoteke "
"za besedo bi bil zgornji desni kot celice te besede označen z rdečo "
"zastavico. Če želite tako, storite enako z drugo besedo para. Če s kazalcem "
"miške premaknete nad to zastavico, se prikažeta ime in pot do zvočne "
"datoteke."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:973
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a sound"
msgstr "Dodajanje zvoka"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering Comparison Forms"
msgstr "Vnos primerjalnih obrazcev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:990
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to enter comparison forms, make sure the comparison forms tool is "
"enabled. You open it with the check box: <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Comparison Forms</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Za vnos primerjalnih obrazcev se prepričajte, da je omogočeno orodje za "
"primerjalne obrazce. Odprete ga s potrditvenim poljem: "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Primerjalni obrazci</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid "First select a word that is an adjective or adverb."
msgstr "Najprej izberite besedo, ki je pridevnik ali prislov."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comparison Forms tool"
msgstr "Orodje Primerjalni obrazci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Adjective</guibutton> or <guibutton>Adverb</guibutton> "
"button in the comparison forms tool."
msgstr ""
"V orodju za primerjalne obrazce pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Pridevnik</"
"guibutton> ali <guibutton>Prislov</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the comparison forms."
msgstr "Vnesite primerjalne obrazce."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1022
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing the comparison forms"
msgstr "Urejanje primerjalnih obrazcev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you can use the <link linkend=\"comparison-forms-of-adjectives-and-"
"adverbs\">Comparison Forms Practice</link> mode."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj lahko uporabite način <link linkend=\"comparison-forms-of-adjectives-"
"and-adverbs\">Vadba primerjalnih oblik</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering Inflection Forms"
msgstr "Vnos pregibnih oblik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to enter inflection forms, make sure the inflection forms tool is "
"enabled. You open it with the check box: <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Inflection (verbs, adjectives, nouns)</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Za vnos pregibnih oblik se prepričajte, da je omogočeno orodje za pregibne "
"oblike. Odprete ga s potrditvenim poljem: <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pregib (glagoli, pridevniki, samostalniki)</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1035
#, no-c-format
msgid "First select a word that is a verb."
msgstr "Najprej izberite besedo, ki je glagol."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1042 index.docbook:1053
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing the inflection forms"
msgstr "Urejanje pregibnih oblik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press on the <guibutton>Verb</guibutton> button in the inflections tool."
msgstr "Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Glagol</guibutton> v orodju za pregibe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After selecting the right tense in the <guilabel>Tense:</guilabel> drop down "
"box, enter the conjugation forms."
msgstr ""
"Ko v spustnem polju <guilabel>Čas:</guilabel> izberete pravi čas, vnesite "
"spregatvene oblike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1060
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tenses can be configured for each language: <link linkend=\"languages-"
"and-grammar\">Languages and Grammar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Čase je mogoče konfigurirati za vsak jezik: <link linkend=\"languages-and-"
"grammar\">Jeziki in slovnica</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1063
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you can use the <link linkend=\"conjugations\">Conjugations Practice</"
"link> mode."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj lahko uporabite način <link linkend=\"conjugations\">Vadba spregatev</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1066
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>Noun</guibutton> or <guibutton>Adjective</guibutton> "
"button to add declension forms to your vocabulary."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <guibutton>Samostalnik</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Pridevnik</"
"guibutton>, da v svoj besednjak dodate sklanjatvene oblike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating New Files"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje novih datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1072
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this section we will describe how to create new files and this not only "
"with the usual vocabulary learning part, but also for grammar exercises, "
"mathematics, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku bomo opisali, kako ustvariti nove datoteke in to ne le z "
"običajnim delom učenja besedišča, ampak tudi za slovnične vaje, matematiko "
"&etc;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1075
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Collection: Vocabulary English-German"
msgstr "Nova zbirka: Besednjak angleško-nemški"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1077
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this section we describe how you can create a vocabulary training file "
"including pictures and sound. In a second stage we will also add adjectives "
"and verbs. This is a very complete example and therefore quite long. "
"Eventually you will not need all points for your project."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku opisujemo, kako lahko ustvarite datoteko za usposabljanje "
"besedišča, vključno s slikami in zvokom. V drugi fazi bomo dodali tudi "
"pridevnike in glagole. To je zelo popoln primer in zato precej dolg. Sčasoma "
"ne boste potrebovali vseh točk za svoj projekt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1080
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since we wish to add sound-files and pictures, we should make sure that "
"these will all be in one folder which for convenience is being called "
"<emphasis>eng-deu</emphasis>. Our data file we create with &parley; will be "
"saved in the same folder. This will help a lot when you decide to share your "
"work with others."
msgstr ""
"Ker želimo dodati zvočne datoteke in slike, se moramo prepričati, da bodo "
"vse v eni mapi, ki se zaradi priročnosti imenuje <emphasis>eng-deu</"
"emphasis>. Naša podatkovna datoteka, ki jo ustvarimo s &parley; bo shranjen "
"v isti mapi. To vam bo zelo pomagalo, ko se boste odločili svoje delo deliti "
"z drugimi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1083
#, no-c-format
msgid "So this is what we have in terms of sound files and pictures:"
msgstr "To je torej tisto, kar imamo v smislu zvočnih datotek in slik:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Data folder in &dolphin;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Mapa s podatki v &dolphin;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid "<caption>Data folder in &dolphin;</caption>"
msgstr "<caption>Podatkovna mapa v &dolphin;</caption>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1094
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's start from the <guilabel>Dashboard</guilabel> which is shown once you "
"launch &parley;:"
msgstr ""
"Začnimo z <guilabel>Nadzorno ploščo</guilabel>, ki se prikaže, ko zaženete "
"&parley;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press on the <guibutton>Create a New Collection...</guibutton> button."
msgstr "Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Ustvari novo zbirko...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>General Document Properties</guilabel> section shows up which "
"is being filled as follows (just adapt to what your file is about):"
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se razdelek <guilabel>Splošne lastnosti dokumenta</guilabel>, ki se "
"polni na naslednji način (samo prilagodite vsebini vaše datoteke):"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1112
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Properties for ... dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Lastnosti za... pogovorno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid "<caption>Properties for ... dialog</caption>"
msgstr "<caption>Lastnosti za pogovorno okno...</caption>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next press on the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button. The following screen "
"asks you to set up the language details. Here we don't want to change "
"anything and therefore we just press on <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Nato pritisnite gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>. Naslednji zaslon "
"zahteva, da nastavite jezikovne podrobnosti. Tukaj ne želimo ničesar "
"spremeniti in zato preprosto pritisnemo <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As a first step, let's create the vocabulary part. We will think about the "
"addition of the sound files and pictures in a second stage. This is what the "
"unit looks like:"
msgstr ""
"Kot prvi korak ustvarimo del besedišča. O dodajanju zvočnih datotek in slik "
"bomo razmišljali v drugi fazi. Enota je videti takole:"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1129
#, no-c-format
msgid "A new empty collection"
msgstr "Nova prazna zbirka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before we do anything else, let's save the file to the folder with the "
"pictures and sound-files. Use the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item and select the folder "
"using the navigation. In this example we will call the file "
"<guilabel>Trainer eng-deu</guilabel> - once you entered the name just press "
"on the <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Preden naredimo karkoli drugega, shranimo datoteko v mapo s slikami in "
"zvočnimi datotekami. Uporabite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in z navigacijo izberite mapo. V tem primeru bomo datoteko "
"imenovali <guilabel>Trainer eng-deu</guilabel> - ko vnesete ime, samo "
"pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Vocabulary As dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Shrani besedišče kot"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving a new collection"
msgstr "Shranjevanje nove zbirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you now check your folder where the sound-files and pictures are, you "
"will also find the file <filename>Trainer eng-deu.kvtml</filename>&nbsp;."
msgstr ""
"Če zdaj preverite svojo mapo, kjer so zvočne datoteke in slike, boste našli "
"tudi datoteko <filename>Trainer eng-deu.kvtml</filename>&nbsp;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's have a short look at the words we want to add: <emphasis>apple, bird, "
"cat, cherry, cow, orange, pear, snake, strawberry</emphasis>. We have "
"animals and fruit and therefore we decide to create two units that are "
"called: <guilabel>Animals</guilabel> and <guilabel>Fruits</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Oglejmo si na kratko besede, ki jih želimo dodati: <emphasis>jabolko, ptica, "
"mačka, češnja, krava, pomaranča, hruška, kača, jagoda</emphasis>. Imamo "
"živali in sadje, zato smo se odločili ustvariti dve enoti, ki se imenujeta: "
"<guilabel>Živali</guilabel> in <guilabel>Sadje</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We now rename <guilabel>Lesson 1</guilabel> to <guilabel>Animals</guilabel> "
"and then we add a unit called <guilabel>Fruits</guilabel>. Click with the "
"&RMB; on the <guilabel>Lesson 1</guilabel> and choose <guimenuitem>Rename "
"Unit</guimenuitem> from the items shown. Now <guilabel>Lesson 1</guilabel> "
"is highlighted and you can simply overwrite it by typing in "
"<guilabel>Animals</guilabel>. When done, press the &Enter; key. Now click "
"with the &RMB; on the <guilabel>Collection: Vocabulary trainer E...</"
"guilabel>, which is the root of the unit tree and choose <guimenuitem>New "
"Unit</guimenuitem> from the items shown. In the new field write "
"<guilabel>Fruits</guilabel> and press the &Enter; key again."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj <guilabel>1. lekcijo</guilabel> preimenujemo v <guilabel>Živali</"
"guilabel> in nato dodamo enoto z imenom <guilabel>Sadje</guilabel>. Kliknite "
"z &RMB; na <guilabel>Lekcija 1</guilabel> in med prikazanimi predmeti "
"izberite <guimenuitem>Preimenuj enoto</guimenuitem>. Zdaj je <guilabel>1. "
"lekcija</guilabel> označena in jo lahko preprosto prepišete tako, da vnesete "
"<guilabel>Živali</guilabel>. Ko končate, pritisnite &Enter; ključ. Zdaj "
"kliknite z &RMB; na <guilabel>Zbirka: Vadnica besedišča E...</guilabel>, ki "
"je koren drevesa enot, in izberite <guimenuitem>Nova enota</guimenuitem> med "
"prikazanimi elementi. V novo polje vpišite <guilabel>Sadje</guilabel> in "
"pritisnite &Enter; ponovno ključ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, let's insert the animals. Please click on the unit <guilabel>Animals</"
"guilabel> and you will get an empty table you can fill in. Click with the "
"&RMB; in the first field, and insert the source terms. Then, insert the "
"target terms in the second column. Once you've inserted all 4 English animal "
"names with their German translation the screen looks like this:"
msgstr ""
"Najprej vstavimo živali. Kliknite na enoto <guilabel>Živali</guilabel> in "
"dobili boste prazno tabelo, ki jo lahko izpolnite. Kliknite z &RMB; v prvo "
"polje in vstavite izvorne izraze. Nato vstavite ciljne izraze v drugi "
"stolpec. Ko vstavite vsa 4 angleška imena živali z nemškim prevodom, je "
"zaslon videti takole:"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1160
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing the vocabulary trainer English-German"
msgstr "Urejanje vadnice besedišča angleščina-nemščina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In our case we want only 4 entries in the animals unit. There are many empty "
"lines that should be deleted. To do this click on the first empty field, and "
"keep the &Shift; key pressed while clicking on the last empty field. All "
"lines to be deleted will be highlighted. Then, press the &Del; key."
msgstr ""
"V našem primeru želimo samo 4 vnose v enoti živali. Obstaja veliko praznih "
"vrstic, ki bi jih bilo treba izbrisati. Če želite to narediti, kliknite na "
"prvo prazno polje in obdržite &Shift; pritisnjena tipka ob kliku na zadnje "
"prazno polje. Vse vrstice, ki jih želite izbrisati, bodo označene. Nato "
"pritisnite tipko &Del;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's add the fruit terminology. Just click on the unit named "
"<guilabel>Fruits</guilabel>. This second unit is completely empty. Since we "
"have five fruit terms we need to add five lines. Therefore, press the &Ins; "
"key five times, and then, just like before, we add our terminology."
msgstr ""
"Dodajmo sadjarsko terminologijo. Kliknite na enoto z imenom <guilabel>Sadje</"
"guilabel>. Ta druga enota je popolnoma prazna. Ker imamo pet sadnih izrazov, "
"moramo dodati pet vrstic. Zato pritisnite &Ins; tipkamo petkrat, nato pa, "
"tako kot prej, dodamo svojo terminologijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Don't forget to save every now and then ..."
msgstr "Ne pozabite občasno shraniti..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A click on the root of our unit tree <guilabel>Collection: Vocabulary "
"trainer E...</guilabel> and &parley; will show us all entries that are "
"present in the two units:"
msgstr ""
"Klik na koren našega drevesa enot <guilabel>Zbirka: Vadnica besedišča E...</"
"guilabel> in &parley; nam bo pokazal vse vnose, ki so prisotni v dveh enotah:"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1180
#, no-c-format
msgid "All entries present in two units"
msgstr "Vsi vnosi so predstavljeni v dveh enotah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Time to add sound and images. First of all we need to activate the "
"<guilabel>Image</guilabel> and <guilabel>Sound</guilabel> views. Select the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Image</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> and <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sound</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> check boxes. Once these options are activated, two "
"new sections are shown as two new tabs on the bottom right hand side of the "
"&parley; editing screen."
msgstr ""
"Čas je, da dodate zvok in slike. Najprej moramo aktivirati pogleda "
"<guilabel>Slika</guilabel> in <guilabel>Zvok</guilabel>. Izberite kljukici "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Slika</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zvok</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> škatle. Ko so te možnosti aktivirane, sta dva nova "
"razdelka prikazana kot dva nova zavihka na spodnji desni strani &parley; "
"zaslon za urejanje."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sound and Image sections"
msgstr "Razdelki Zvok in Slika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the English word <emphasis>apple</emphasis> by clicking on it. It is "
"highlighted, so let's add the picture. In the image section on the right "
"hand side press on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"folder-black.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Folder</guiicon> icon and choose the picture you wish to associate."
msgstr ""
"Izberite angleško besedo <emphasis>apple</emphasis> s klikom nanjo. "
"Poudarjeno je, zato dodamo sliko. V razdelku s slikami na desni strani "
"pritisnite <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"folder-black."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Mapa</"
"guiicon> in izberite sliko, ki jo želite povezati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add the pronunciation for the English apple, do the same in the Sound "
"section, selecting the relevant sound file."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati izgovorjavo za angleško jabolko, storite enako v razdelku "
"Zvok in izberite ustrezno zvočno datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By pressing on the <guibutton>Play</guibutton> button in the sound tool you "
"can listen to the pronunciation."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Predvajaj</guibutton> v zvočnem orodju lahko "
"poslušate izgovorjavo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1204
#, no-c-format
msgid "The screen will then look like this:"
msgstr "Zaslon bo nato videti takole:"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing the sound"
msgstr "Predvajanje zvoka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then click on the German translation <guilabel>Apfel</guilabel>. The field "
"is now highlighted to indicate the selection. You will note the picture with "
"the apple is associated also to the German term. In the sound section select "
"the pronunciation, just like before."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite nemški prevod <guilabel>Apfel</guilabel>. Polje je zdaj "
"označeno, kar označuje izbiro. Opazili boste, da je slika z jabolkom "
"povezana tudi z nemškim izrazom. V razdelku zvok izberite izgovorjavo, tako "
"kot prej."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checking the data bonding"
msgstr "Preverjanje povezovanja podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Just go ahead like this for all terms."
msgstr "Kar tako naprej za vse izraze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Time to add adjectives and verbs as units to our project. So just do as "
"before with the unit <emphasis>Fruits</emphasis> and create two new units: "
"<emphasis>Adjectives</emphasis> and <emphasis>Verbs</emphasis>. Let's assume "
"we will add <emphasis>big, small, old, young, narrow</emphasis> in the "
"adjective unit and <emphasis>to go, to come, to buy, to drink, to eat</"
"emphasis> in the verb unit."
msgstr ""
"Čas je, da v naš projekt dodamo pridevnike in glagole kot enote. Torej "
"naredite kot prej z enoto <emphasis>Sadje</emphasis> in ustvarite dve novi "
"enoti: <emphasis>Pridevniki</emphasis> in <emphasis>Glagoli</emphasis>. "
"Recimo, da bomo dodali <emphasis>velik, majhen, star, mlad, ozek</emphasis> "
"v pridevniško enoto in <emphasis>iti, priti, kupiti, piti, jesti</emphasis> "
"v glagolu enota."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following shows a screenshot with all inserted terminology. Now, words "
"are mixed and it would be nice to see what is a <emphasis>noun, adjective</"
"emphasis> or <emphasis>verb</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Sledi posnetek zaslona z vso vstavljeno terminologijo. Zdaj so besede "
"pomešane in lepo bi bilo videti, kaj je <emphasis>samostalnik, pridevnik</"
"emphasis> ali <emphasis>glagol</emphasis>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows all inserted terminology"
msgstr "Prikazuje vso vstavljeno terminologijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As the next step we are going to show the <guilabel>Word Type</guilabel>. "
"Select the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vocabulary "
"Columns</guimenuitem></menuchoice> check box. We activate <guilabel>Word "
"Type</guilabel> for <emphasis>English</emphasis> and <emphasis>German</"
"emphasis> by clicking on the check box in front of <guilabel>Word Type</"
"guilabel>. Then press on the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button to accept the "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"Kot naslednji korak bomo prikazali <guilabel>Vrsto besede</guilabel>. "
"Izberite potrditveno polje <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Stolpci besedišča</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. <guilabel>Besedno "
"vrsto</guilabel> aktiviramo za <emphasis>angleščino</emphasis> in "
"<emphasis>nemščino</emphasis> s klikom na potrditveno polje pred "
"<guilabel>Besedno vrsto</guilabel>. Nato pritisnite gumb <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton>, da sprejmete spremembe."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Word Type item"
msgstr "Izbira elementa besedna vrsta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By clicking on the fields in the column <guilabel>Word Type</guilabel> you "
"can select the word type and for those languages where nouns have a gender "
"you can also select the <emphasis>Noun/Gender</emphasis> combination. "
"Alternatively start to type the first characters of a word type to select "
"it. Below the <guilabel>Word Type</guilabel> column with part of the "
"selections already done."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na polja v stolpcu <guilabel>Besedna vrsta</guilabel> lahko "
"izberete besedno vrsto in za tiste jezike, kjer imajo samostalniki spol, "
"lahko izberete tudi kombinacijo <emphasis>Samostalnik/Spol</emphasis>. Druga "
"možnost je, da začnete vnašati prve znake besedne vrste, da jo izberete. Pod "
"stolpcem <guilabel>Besedna vrsta</guilabel> z delom že opravljenih izbir."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing the Word Types"
msgstr "Izbira besednih vrst"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once we have specified all the word types, we will first consider "
"<emphasis>Adjectives</emphasis>, adding <guilabel>Comparison forms</"
"guilabel> to them. So let's move to the <emphasis>Adjectives</emphasis> unit "
"only."
msgstr ""
"Ko določimo vse besedne vrste, bomo najprej razmislili o "
"<emphasis>pridevnikih</emphasis> in jim dodali <guilabel>primerjalne oblike</"
"guilabel>. Torej pojdimo samo na enoto <emphasis>Pridevniki</emphasis>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting the comparison forms"
msgstr "Izbira primerjalnih obrazcev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To show the <guilabel>Comparison Forms</guilabel> on the right hand side of "
"the screen, select the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Comparison Forms</guimenuitem></menuchoice> check box."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz <guilabel>Primerjalnih obrazcev</guilabel> na desni strani zaslona "
"izberite potrditveno polje <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Primerjalni obrazci</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows the comparison forms"
msgstr "Prikazuje primerjalne obrazce"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Edit the <guilabel>Comparison Forms</guilabel> by adding "
"<guilabel>Comparative</guilabel> and <guilabel>Superlative</guilabel> to the "
"single adjectives. First, click on the adjective for which you wish to add "
"the comparison forms, in our case <emphasis>big</emphasis>, and add "
"<emphasis>bigger</emphasis> and <emphasis>biggest</emphasis>. Then, continue "
"with the next adjective to complete, until all comparison forms have been "
"entered."
msgstr ""
"Uredite <guilabel>Primerjalne oblike</guilabel> tako, da posameznim "
"pridevnikom dodate <guilabel>Primerjalnik</guilabel> in <guilabel>Vsežnik</"
"guilabel>. Najprej kliknite na pridevnik, za katerega želite dodati "
"primerjalne oblike, v našem primeru <emphasis>velik</emphasis>, in dodajte "
"<emphasis>večji</emphasis> in <emphasis>največji</emphasis>. Nato nadaljujte "
"z naslednjim pridevnikom, ki ga želite dokončati, dokler ne vnesete vseh "
"primerjalnih oblik."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding the Comparative and Superlative"
msgstr "Dodajanje primerjalnika in presežnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, let's consider the conjugation form of the <guilabel>Verbs</"
"guilabel>. Select the <guilabel>Verbs</guilabel> unit and then activate the "
"inflection section on the right hand side by selecting the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Inflection (verbs, "
"adjectives, nouns)</guimenuitem></menuchoice> check box. As an example we "
"edit the present tense (<guilabel>Präsens</guilabel>) form of "
"<emphasis>gehen</emphasis>. Please first select <guilabel>Präsens</guilabel> "
"from the drop down box and then add the verb forms."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu si oglejmo spregatveno obliko <guilabel>glagolov</guilabel>. "
"Izberite enoto <guilabel>Glagoli</guilabel> in nato aktivirajte razdelek za "
"pregib na desni strani tako, da izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pregib (glagoli, pridevniki, samostalniki)</"
"guimenuitem ></menuchoice> potrditveno polje. Kot primer uredimo obliko "
"sedanjika (<guilabel>Präsens</guilabel>) za <emphasis>gehen</emphasis>. "
"Najprej izberite <guilabel>Präsens</guilabel> v spustnem meniju in nato "
"dodajte glagolske oblike."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing the conjugation form of the verb"
msgstr "Izbira spregatvene oblike glagola"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1309
#, no-c-format
msgid "This needs to be done for all verbs, and in all possible tenses."
msgstr "To je treba narediti za vse glagole in v vseh možnih časih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you are done you can start to practice by pressing on the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-start.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <link linkend="
"\"vocabulary-practice\"><guiicon>Practice</guiicon></link> icon in the "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate, lahko začnete vaditi s pritiskom na "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-start.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <link linkend="
"\"vocabulary-practice\"><guiicon>Vaja</guiicon></link> ikona v orodni "
"vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Collection: Single Names and Collective Names"
msgstr "Nova zbirka: posamezna imena in skupna imena"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This exercise was created for the 3rd class of an Italian primary school. "
"Pupils are supposed to connect single names with collective names, such as "
"<emphasis>tree</emphasis> → <emphasis>woods</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"Ta vaja je bila ustvarjena za 3. razred italijanske osnovne šole. Učenci naj "
"posamezna imena povezujejo s zbirnimi imeni, kot je <emphasis>drevo</"
"emphasis> → <emphasis>gozd</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &parley; you get the start page, eventually also listing some "
"previously used files (that you cannot see here)."
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete &parley; dobite začetno stran, sčasoma tudi seznam nekaterih "
"predhodno uporabljenih datotek (ki jih tukaj ne morete videti)."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1328
#, no-c-format
msgid "<caption>Dashboard</caption>"
msgstr "<caption>Nadzorna plošča</caption>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press on the <guibutton>Create a New Collection...</guibutton> button and "
"the following screen with empty or partly filled fields will show up:"
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Ustvari novo zbirko...</guibutton> in prikazal se "
"bo naslednji zaslon s praznimi ali delno izpolnjenimi polji:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1336
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Properties for Untitled dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Lastnosti za pogovorno okno brez naslova</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1339
#, no-c-format
msgid "<caption>Properties for Untitled dialog</caption>"
msgstr "<caption>Lastnosti za pogovorno okno brez naslova</caption>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fill in the title, here <guilabel>nomi singoli e collettivi</guilabel>, your "
"name, email address, in the <guilabel>Comment:</guilabel> text box you can "
"write down a more detailed description, select your <guilabel>Category:</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>License:</guilabel>. Then there we have something "
"special: instead of indicating the <guilabel>First language:</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Second language:</guilabel>, like it normally would happen, we "
"added <emphasis>nome singolo</emphasis> (single name) and <emphasis>nome "
"collettivo</emphasis> (collective name). The <guilabel>Setup grammar "
"details</guilabel> and <guilabel>Download grammar</guilabel> options are not "
"needed here. In the screenshot they are still activated - please deactivate "
"them by just clicking on the check boxes. When you are done, please press on "
"the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite naslov, tukaj <guilabel>nomi singoli e collettivi</guilabel>, vaše "
"ime, e-poštni naslov, v besedilno polje <guilabel>Komentar:</guilabel> lahko "
"zapišete podrobnejši opis, izberite svoj <guilabel >Kategorija:</guilabel> "
"in <guilabel>Licenca:</guilabel>. Potem imamo nekaj posebnega: namesto "
"označevanja <guilabel>Prvi jezik:</guilabel> in <guilabel>Drugi jezik:</"
"guilabel>, kot bi se običajno zgodilo, smo dodali <emphasis>nome singolo</"
"emphasis> (enotno ime) in <emphasis>nome collettivo</emphasis> (skupno ime). "
"Možnosti <guilabel>Nastavi slovnične podrobnosti</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Prenesi slovnico</guilabel> tukaj nista potrebni. Na posnetku "
"zaslona so še vedno aktivirani - deaktivirajte jih tako, da preprosto "
"kliknete potrditvena polja. Ko končate, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Languages...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item and the <guilabel>Properties for nome "
"singolo</guilabel> section comes up and here you see it already with the "
"necessary changes made:"
msgstr ""
"Izberite menijski element <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Jeziki ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in prikaže se razdelek "
"<guilabel>Lastnosti za nome singolo</guilabel> in tukaj vidite je že s "
"potrebnimi spremembami:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1350 index.docbook:1364
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Languages dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za urejanje jezikov"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties for nome singolo"
msgstr "Lastnosti za nome singolo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left hand side you can see where the data you are adding belongs to. "
"<emphasis>nome singolo</emphasis>. Choose the language, here "
"<emphasis>Italian</emphasis> and insert <emphasis>nome singolo</emphasis> in "
"the following editable field. Then press on the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani lahko vidite, kam sodijo podatki, ki jih dodajate. "
"<emphasis>nome singolo</emphasis>. Izberite jezik, tukaj "
"<emphasis>italijanščino</emphasis> in vnesite <emphasis>nome singolo</"
"emphasis> v naslednje polje za urejanje. Nato pritisnite gumb <guibutton>V "
"redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now the <guilabel>Properties for nome collettivo</guilabel> section is shown:"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj je prikazan razdelek <guilabel>Lastnosti za nome collettivo</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1367
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties for nome collettivo"
msgstr "Lastnosti za nome collettivo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like before: choose <guilabel>Italian</guilabel> as language and insert "
"<emphasis>nome collettivo</emphasis> and press on the <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Kot prej: izberite <guilabel>italijanščino</guilabel> kot jezik in vstavite "
"<emphasis>nome collettivo</emphasis> ter pritisnite gumb <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid "And now you can start to edit:"
msgstr "In zdaj lahko začnete urejati:"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a new practice collective"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje novega vadbenega kolektiva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Just insert the <emphasis>nome singolo</emphasis> (single name) in the first "
"column and the corresponding <emphasis>nome collettivo</emphasis> "
"(collective name) in the second column."
msgstr ""
"Preprosto vstavite <emphasis>nome singolo</emphasis> (enotno ime) v prvi "
"stolpec in ustrezno <emphasis>nome collettivo</emphasis> (skupno ime) v "
"drugi stolpec."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a new entry"
msgstr "Dodajanje novega vnosa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the number of available fields is not enough, just click with the &RMB; "
"anywhere on the edit section and choose <guimenuitem>Add New Entry</"
"guimenuitem>. Don't forget to save your file every now and then. When you "
"have finished adding all entries you will want to see if Practice mode works "
"fine. Well just press on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"practice-start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Practice</guiicon> icon in the toolbar right "
"above the edit section and the page with the practice settings comes up:"
msgstr ""
"Če število razpoložljivih polj ni dovolj, kliknite z &RMB; kjer koli v "
"razdelku za urejanje in izberite <guimenuitem>Dodaj nov vnos</guimenuitem>. "
"Ne pozabite občasno shraniti datoteke. Ko končate z dodajanjem vseh vnosov, "
"boste želeli preveriti, ali način za vajo deluje dobro. Samo pritisnite "
"ikono <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"practice-start.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Vaja</"
"guiicon> v desni orodni vrstici nad razdelkom za urejanje in prikaže se "
"stran z nastavitvami vadbe:"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1403
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiple Choice Practice Mode"
msgstr "Način vadbe z več izbirami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this case <guilabel>Multiple Choice</guilabel> is a good option, but also "
"<guilabel>Written</guilabel> will do fine. After choosing the Practice Mode "
"just press on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"practice-start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Start Practice...</guiicon> icon in the toolbar and have fun."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru je <guilabel>Večkratna izbira</guilabel> dobra možnost, vendar "
"bo tudi <guilabel>Napisano</guilabel> dobro. Ko izberete način za vadbo, "
"samo pritisnite <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"practice-start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Začni vajo...</guiicon> v orodni vrstici in se zabavajte."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1412
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting Additional Collections"
msgstr "Pridobivanje dodatnih zbirk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are on the <guilabel>Dashboard</guilabel> you have the possibility "
"to install collections directly from the server, provided you are online. "
"Just press on the <guibutton>Download New Collections...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste na <guilabel>Nadzorni plošči</guilabel>, imate možnost namestiti "
"zbirke neposredno s strežnika, če ste povezani. Samo pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Prenesi nove zbirke...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A window with many interesting collections opens. Just select what you find "
"most interesting and press on the <guibutton>Install</guibutton> button. "
"Then open the file to practice or edit."
msgstr ""
"Odpre se okno s številnimi zanimivimi zbirkami. Samo izberite tisto, kar se "
"vam zdi najbolj zanimivo, in pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Namesti</guibutton>. "
"Nato odprite datoteko za vadbo ali urejanje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1429
#, no-c-format
msgid "Download New Stuff dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za prenos novih stvari"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting new collections"
msgstr "Pridobivanje novih zbirk"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1437
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &parley;"
msgstr "Konfiguriraj &parley;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure the appearance of &parley; from the <guilabel>Dashboard</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Practice</guilabel>, or <guilabel>Editor</guilabel> "
"screens. Select the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &parley;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirate lahko videz &parley; z zaslonov <guilabel>Nadzorna plošča</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Vaja</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Urejevalnik</guilabel>. "
"Izberite menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &parley;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1442
#, no-c-format
msgid "Theme Page"
msgstr "Tematska stran"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configuration opens with the <guilabel>Theme</guilabel> page. This is "
"the place where you can choose how &parley; should greet you when launching "
"it: an elegant <guilabel>Gray</guilabel> version or the all time busy "
"<guilabel>Bees</guilabel>. Note that it could well be that <guilabel>Fluffy "
"Bunny</guilabel> is not in your version: if you want it, read the following "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracija se odpre s stranjo <guilabel>Tema</guilabel>. To je kraj, kjer "
"lahko izberete, kako &parley; naj vas pozdravi ob zagonu: elegantna "
"<guilabel>Siva</guilabel> različica ali ves čas zaposlene <guilabel>Čebele</"
"guilabel>. Upoštevajte, da se lahko zgodi, da <guilabel>Fluffy Bunny</"
"guilabel> ni v vaši različici: če ga želite, preberite naslednji razdelek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you selected your preferred theme, press on the <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete želeno temo, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1450
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the <guilabel>Bees</guilabel> theme:"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona teme <guilabel>Čebele</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training screen"
msgstr "Zaslon za usposabljanje"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1457
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bees theme in action"
msgstr "Tema Čebele v akciji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"And if these are not enough: you can press on the <guibutton>Get New "
"Themes...</guibutton> button to find more themes. Over time we hope that "
"more and more themes come along. If you know how to create &SVG; graphics "
"(for example with <ulink url=\"https://inkscape.org\"><application>Inkscape</"
"application></ulink>), you can create your own theme and share it with the "
"world."
msgstr ""
"In če to ni dovolj: lahko pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Pridobi nove teme...</"
"guibutton>, da poiščete več tem. Sčasoma upamo, da bo na voljo vedno več "
"tem. Če veste, kako ustvariti &SVG; grafike (na primer z <ulink url="
"\"https://inkscape.org\"><application>Inkscape</application></ulink>), lahko "
"ustvarite svojo temo in jo delite s svetom."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1465 index.docbook:1496 index.docbook:1511
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure - &parley; dialog"
msgstr "Konfiguriraj - &parley; dialog"

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Theme settings page"
msgstr "Stran z nastavitvami teme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional themes can be found on <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org/browse/"
"cat/357/order/latest/\">store.kde.org</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Dodatne teme najdete na <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org/browse/cat/357/"
"order/latest/\">store.kde.org</ulink>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1476
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Page"
msgstr "Splošna stran"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>General</guilabel> page gives you some options regarding the "
"behavior of &parley;."
msgstr ""
"Stran <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> vam ponuja nekaj možnosti glede delovanja "
"&parley;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open/Save section"
msgstr "Odpri/Shrani razdelek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Always load the last opened collection on start</guilabel> will "
"immediately take you back to the vocabulary you were learning. Often you "
"will use this together with the second option <guilabel>Save vocabularies "
"automatically on close and quit</guilabel> because it's just handy not to "
"have always answer the same question if changes (including learning results) "
"should be changed or not. The option <guilabel>Create a backup every ... "
"minutes</guilabel> can be very handy to help you save your work frequently. "
"One less thing to think about."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ob zagonu vedno naloži zadnjo odprto zbirko</guilabel> vas bo "
"takoj vrnilo k besedišču, ki ste se ga učili. To boste pogosto uporabljali "
"skupaj z drugo možnostjo <guilabel >Samodejno shrani besednjake ob zaprtju "
"in izhodu</guilabel>, ker je preprosto priročno, da ne odgovarjate vedno na "
"isto vprašanje, ali je treba spremembe (vključno z učnimi rezultati) "
"spremeniti ali ne. Možnost <guilabel>Ustvari varnostno kopijo vsakih ... "
"minut</guilabel> je lahko zelo priročna, saj vam pomaga pri pogostem "
"shranjevanju vašega dela. Ena stvar manj za razmišljanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes the import and/or export of text (CSV) files can be very handy and "
"there you need the proper separator to elaborate data afterwards or to be "
"able to read the data you got from somewhere else. &parley; allows you to "
"choose among various separators to make sure you can re-use your data."
msgstr ""
"Včasih je lahko uvoz in/ali izvoz besedilnih (CSV) datotek zelo priročen in "
"tam potrebujete ustrezno ločilo za naknadno obdelavo podatkov ali za branje "
"podatkov, ki ste jih dobili od nekje drugje. &parley; vam omogoča izbiro med "
"različnimi ločili, da zagotovite ponovno uporabo svojih podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing section"
msgstr "Oddelek za urejanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can determine whether &parley; automatically appends new rows while "
"you are editing your vocabulary collection. This can be useful if you want "
"to add many entries, before then splitting them up into various units. On "
"the other hand, it can be good to have this option off if you want to work "
"by creating units with a set maximum number of entries."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko ugotovite, ali &parley; samodejno doda nove vrstice, medtem ko "
"urejate svojo zbirko besedišča. To je lahko uporabno, če želite dodati "
"veliko vnosov, preden jih razdelite na različne enote. Po drugi strani pa je "
"lahko dobro, če to možnost izklopite, če želite delati z ustvarjanjem enot z "
"nastavljenim največjim številom vnosov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1505
#, no-c-format
msgid "View page"
msgstr "Ogled strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>View</guilabel> page allows you to change font and size for "
"the pronunciation symbols, and you can choose the <guilabel>Base color for "
"displaying grades:</guilabel> you like best."
msgstr ""
"Stran <guilabel>Pogled</guilabel> vam omogoča spreminjanje pisave in "
"velikosti izgovornih simbolov in lahko izberete <guilabel>osnovno barvo za "
"prikaz ocen:</guilabel> vam je najbolj všeč."

#. Tag: caption
#: index.docbook:1514
#, no-c-format
msgid "View settings page"
msgstr "Ogled strani z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notes For Advanced Users"
msgstr "Opombe za napredne uporabnike"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Upload and Share Collections"
msgstr "Naložite in delite zbirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1562
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can upload your files and share them with others."
msgstr "Svoje datoteke lahko naložite in jih delite z drugimi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Upload Vocabulary "
"Document</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item in the <guilabel>Editor</"
"guilabel> within &parley;."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Naloži slovarski dokument</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v "
"<guilabel>Urejevalniku</guilabel> znotraj &parley;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1568
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If that does not work, you can also visit <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org/"
"\">store.kde.org</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če to ne deluje, lahko obiščete tudi <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org/"
"\">store.kde.org</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In either case the files will show up in the <guilabel>Download New Stuff</"
"guilabel> dialog by pressing the <guibutton>Download New Collections...</"
"guibutton> button on the <guilabel>Dashboard</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"V obeh primerih se bodo datoteke prikazale v pogovornem oknu "
"<guilabel>Prenos novih stvari</guilabel> s pritiskom gumba <guibutton>Prenos "
"novih zbirk...</guibutton> na <guilabel>Nadzorni plošči</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1575
#, no-c-format
msgid "File format"
msgstr "Format datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are interested in the file formats that &parley; can read and stores "
"the vocabulary collections in, visit:"
msgstr ""
"Če vas zanimajo formati datotek, ki jih &parley; lahko bere in shranjuje "
"zbirke besedišča v, obiščite:"

#. Tag: ulink
#: index.docbook:1580
#, no-c-format
msgid "&parley; File Formats on userbase.kde.org"
msgstr "&parley; Formati datotek na userbase.kde.org"

